      "id": "PopularPost312276",
      "post_content": "For future wanderers to this card, this was a part of a cycle:  \n  \n[Voice of Grace](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voice of Grace) (*Urza's Saga*)  \n[Voice of Law](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voice of Law) (*Urza's Saga*)  \n  \n[Voice of Reason](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voice of Reason) (*Urza's Destiny*)  \n[Voice of Duty](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voice of Duty) (*Urza's Destiny*)  \n  \n[Voice of Truth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voice of Truth) (*Nemesis*)  \n  \n[Voice of All](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voice of All) (*Planeshift*)  \n  \nAs for the card itself, protection from red is one of the more useful ones, since direct damage is red's primary means of removal. A resilient flyer could potentially cause problems for an opponent who relies on [LIghtning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=LIghtning Bolt) and [Pyroclasm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyroclasm) variants to get rid of creatures.",
      "posted_by": "Equinox523",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost312276\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">For future wanderers to this card, this was a part of a cycle:<br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Voice of Grace\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voice of Grace\">Voice of Grace</a> (<i>Urza's Saga</i>)<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Voice of Law\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voice of Law\">Voice of Law</a> (<i>Urza's Saga</i>)<br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Voice of Reason\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voice of Reason\">Voice of Reason</a> (<i>Urza's Destiny</i>)<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Voice of Duty\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voice of Duty\">Voice of Duty</a> (<i>Urza's Destiny</i>)<br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Voice of Truth\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voice of Truth\">Voice of Truth</a> (<i>Nemesis</i>)<br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Voice of All\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voice of All\">Voice of All</a> (<i>Planeshift</i>)<br/><br/>As for the card itself, protection from red is one of the more useful ones, since direct damage is red's primary means of removal.  A resilient flyer could potentially cause problems for an opponent who relies on <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"LIghtning Bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=LIghtning Bolt\">LIghtning Bolt</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Pyroclasm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyroclasm\">Pyroclasm</a> variants to get rid of creatures.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '312276'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy1136\">Equinox523</span>\r\n                                (4/26/2013 6:52:16 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
